- **Claude Global Plans Fallback**: `~/.claude/plans/` (only for non-project contexts)

### Insights CLI tools

Snapshot system shipped 2026-04-30 (commit `d6aeb8e4`):
- `insights-snapshot [--only-if-newer] [--quiet]` — archive `/insights report.html` immutably
- `insights-list` — chronological one-line summary
- `insights-diff [old] [new]` — compare two snapshots
- `insights-drift [--since DATE] [--narrative-only]` — multi-snapshot trajectory

A SessionEnd hook (entry #5 in `private_dot_claude/settings.json.tmpl`) auto-archives the report
before the rolling-window overwrite.

